results.name: Decimal expansion of tan(1/7).
comment: By the Lindemann-Weierstrass theorem, this constant is transcendental. - _Charles R Greathouse IV_, May 13 2019
link: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..20000
program: (PARI) default(realprecision, 20080); x=10*tan(1/7); for (n=0, 20000, d=floor(x); x=(x-d)*10; write("b161016.txt", n, " ", d));
results.author: _Harry J. Smith_, Jun 14 2009
